folmap = folium.Map([A,B], zoom_start =7, tiles = 'Stamen Terrain', attr ='&copy')

In [35]:
AvLat = df['Latitude'].mean()
AvLong = df['Longitude'].mean()
print(AvLat)
print(AvLong)
#folium map
bts = folium.Map(location =[AvLat,AvLong],zoom_start = 10)

# feature group
two_G = folium.FeatureGroup(name = 'GSM')
three_G = folium.FeatureGroup(name = 'UMTS')
four_G = folium.FeatureGroup(name = 'LTE')
for i in range(0, len(gsm)):
    t=folium.Marker([gsm.iloc[i]['Latitude'], gsm.iloc[i]['Longitude']],
                 icon = folium.Icon(color = 'red', icon = 'ok-sign'), tooltip = gsm.iloc[i]['BTSName'])
    t.add_to(two_G)
for i in range(0, len(umts)):
    p=folium.Marker([umts.iloc[i]['Latitude'], umts.iloc[i]['Longitude']],
                 icon = folium.Icon(color = 'green', icon = 'ok-sign'), tooltip = umts.iloc[i]['BTSName'])
    p.add_to(three_G)
for i in range(0, len(lte)):
    l=folium.Marker([lte.iloc[i]['Latitude'], lte.iloc[i]['Longitude']],
                 icon = folium.Icon(color = 'blue', icon = 'ok-sign'), tooltip = lte.iloc[i]['BTSName'])
    l.add_to(four_G)

two_G.add_to(bts)
three_G.add_to(bts)
four_G.add_to(bts)

bts.add_child(folium.LatLngPopup())
folium.LayerControl().add_to(bts)
bts
